metadata.name: TheBetterPASS #1
metadata.description:
TheBetterPASS by TheBetterNFTs.com is a limited edition release of 350 TheBetterNFTs Gen 1 Utility Pass residing on the Ethereum Blockchain. TheBetterPASS holders get unmatched & exclusive discounts, passive income opportunities on the NFT Management & Blockchain service packages offered by TheBetterNFTs.com. Along with this the holders get free NFTs through giveaways, whitelist access & more perks & utilities.
